[!] RST received: 1.1.1.1:47580   ← bị tấn công
[-] Disconnected: 1.1.1.1:47580   total=0
```

**Client log:**
```
[-] S1 RST    (TCP reset by attacker)
[~] S1 reconnecting in 3s...
[-] S1 RST    (TCP reset by attacker)   ← Stage 4 block
```

**Attacker log:**
```
[+] Kill #1: NAT:56702  RST×2 sent
[+] Kill #2: NAT:57341  RST×2 sent
[~] Carpet sweep #10 (282330 pkts total)
```

